CursedCore is a World of Warcraft game server emulator. It is derived
from CactusEmu which is derived from Trinity Core, itself derived from MaNGOS. 
CursedCore is based on their code, and CursedCore will or may have custom code
in which you can use at your own risk =] The Cursed Project is inteded for learning
purposes only. It is not intended for the following:
a. A private or public server.
b. Abuse in any shape or form.
c. NOT TO BE USED AS A MEANS OF HACKING!


API documentation can be obtained by running the "make doc" command inside
the doc directory.

SQL files to create the database can be found in the sql directory. Files
to update your database from an older revision/version can be found in the
sql/updates directory.

The extractor *needs* that you finished *all* the updates of the client.
It includes the small updates at the end.
You should also verify that the accountType setting is set to "CT" in your WTF/launcher.wtf and WTF/config.wtf.

At this time Cursed does not support Linux
